v> <div class="entry-footer"> <div class="entry-meta"> <div class="entry-author"><span>Author: </span><span class="vcard author author_name"><span class="fn"><a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/author/homeandplateadmin/" title="Posts by Ali Randall" rel="author">Ali Randall</a></span></span></div> <div class="entry-category"><span>Filed Under: </span><a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/category/baked-goods/" rel="category tag">Baked Goods</a>, <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/category/sweets/" rel="category tag">Sweets</a></div> <div class="entry-tags"><span>Tags: </span><a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/tag/christmas/" rel="tag">Christmas</a>, <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/tag/christmas-cookies/" rel="tag">Christmas cookies</a>, <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/tag/cookies/" rel="tag">Cookies</a>, <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/tag/holiday-recipes/" rel="tag">Holiday Recipes</a></div> </div>  <div class="entry-share"> </div>  </div> </div>  <hr /> <div class="pagination-post"> <div class="previous_post"><a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/key-lime-yogurt-parfait-with-granola/" rel="prev">The Best Key Lime Yogurt Parfait (Easy Recipe)</a></div> <div class="next_post"><a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/salted-nut-brittle/" rel="next">The Best Homemade Salted Nut Brittle</a></div> </div>  <hr /> <div id="comments" class="comments"> <h3 class="comment-title"> 14 thoughts on &ldquo;Perfect Sugar Cookie Recipe for Decorating&rdquo; </h3> <ul class="comment-list"> <li id="comment-4916" class="comment even thread-even depth-1 parent"> <article id="div-comment-4916" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Jacqueline Debono</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4916"><time datetime="2019-12-18T18:13:53+00:00">December 18, 2019 at 6:13 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p><img alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" class="wprm-comment-rating nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTcwNDoxODY=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTcwNDoxODY=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTIwIDI0IiB3aWR0aD0iMTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjI0IiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" /><br /> These sugar cookies are going on my Christmas cookie list. I love all the ways they can be decorated!</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-4932" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-2"> <article id="div-comment-4932" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4932"><time datetime="2019-12-19T12:33:15+00:00">December 19, 2019 at 12:33 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>Thanks so much Jacqueline. That is the best part of this recipe, at least for my kids. Wait&#8230; eating them is:)</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> </li> <li id="comment-4917" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 parent"> <article id="div-comment-4917" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">stephanie</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4917"><time datetime="2019-12-18T18:23:25+00:00">December 18, 2019 at 6:23 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p><img alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" class="wprm-comment-rating nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTc0MToxODY=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTc0MToxODY=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTIwIDI0IiB3aWR0aD0iMTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjI0IiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" /><br /> Me and my son had so much fun making these and even more fun eating them. I will be making more for Christmas,</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-4931" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-2"> <article id="div-comment-4931" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4931"><time datetime="2019-12-19T12:32:30+00:00">December 19, 2019 at 12:32 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>They are perfect for kid time in the kitchen. And they always get eaten. A second day of baking is always in order 🙂</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> </li> <li id="comment-4918" class="comment even thread-even depth-1 parent"> <article id="div-comment-4918" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Heidy L. McCallum</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4918"><time datetime="2019-12-18T18:41:55+00:00">December 18, 2019 at 6:41 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p><img alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" class="wprm-comment-rating nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTc3ODoxODY=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTc3ODoxODY=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTIwIDI0IiB3aWR0aD0iMTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjI0IiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" /><br /> These were so wonderful. they turned out perfect for our holiday cookie swap at the office.</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-4930" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-2"> <article id="div-comment-4930" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4930"><time datetime="2019-12-19T12:31:10+00:00">December 19, 2019 at 12:31 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>So glad these worked for you so well. These are always hit in my house.</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> </li> <li id="comment-4919" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 parent"> <article id="div-comment-4919" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Karen @ Seasonal Cravings</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4919"><time datetime="2019-12-18T18:42:43+00:00">December 18, 2019 at 6:42 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p><img alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" class="wprm-comment-rating nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTgxNToxODY=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTgxNToxODY=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTIwIDI0IiB3aWR0aD0iMTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjI0IiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" /><br /> It&#8217;s so funny that I have so many sugar cookies recipes but not one go to recipe. I don&#8217;t have one that is a no fail. This one looks perfect and they are so many helpful instructions and photos that I almost can&#8217;t fail. Love how you decorated them especially the reindeer!</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-4929" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-2"> <article id="div-comment-4929" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-4929"><time datetime="2019-12-19T12:30:30+00:00">December 19, 2019 at 12:30 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>Thanks Karen. I have lots of sugar cookie recipes too but this one is my go-to. It&#8217;s definitely no-fail!</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> </li> <li id="comment-6412" class="comment even thread-even depth-1 parent"> <article id="div-comment-6412" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Linda Brown</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-6412"><time datetime="2020-11-25T14:20:58+00:00">November 25, 2020 at 2:20 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>I don’t know that I can rate, not having made and eaten them yet, but I was wondering if almond flour can be used for my gluten free friends. Recipe looks easy and delicious. Thanks!</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-6413" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-2 parent"> <article id="div-comment-6413" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-6413"><time datetime="2020-11-25T14:50:37+00:00">November 25, 2020 at 2:50 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>Hi Linda. It&#8217;s not as simple as swapping almond flour for all purpose because almond flour needs more egg or a type of binder. I would suggest using a gluten free flour instead like this one from Bob&#8217;s https://www.bobsredmill.com/gluten-free-1-to-1-baking-flour.html</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-6414" class="comment even depth-3 parent"> <article id="div-comment-6414" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Linda Brown</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-6414"><time datetime="2020-11-25T18:39:40+00:00">November 25, 2020 at 6:39 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>Thanks very much. One other thing. What is the yield of this recipe? I realize it depends on the size of the cookie, but maybe a medium size as your picture appears to be. Thanks again!</p> </div> </article> <ul class="children"> <li id="comment-6415" class="comment byuser comment-author-homeandplateadmin bypostauthor odd alt depth-4"> <article id="div-comment-6415" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Ali Randall</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-6415"><time datetime="2020-11-25T19:05:59+00:00">November 25, 2020 at 7:05 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>This recipe makes about two to three dozen cookies depending of size. Good luck and let me know how they turn out 🙂</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> </li> </ul> </li> </ul> </li> <li id="comment-8689" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1"> <article id="div-comment-8689" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Rosse</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-8689"><time datetime="2022-09-19T14:02:50+00:00">September 19, 2022 at 2:02 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p><img alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" class="wprm-comment-rating nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTkyNjoxODY=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTkyNjoxODY=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTIwIDI0IiB3aWR0aD0iMTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjI0IiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" /><br /> I tried this recipe and it turned out really good. Thanks for the recipe.<br /> &nbsp;</p> </div> </article> </li> <li id="comment-8759" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1"> <article id="div-comment-8759" class="comment-body"> <footer class="comment-meta nitro-lazy"> <div class="comment-author vcard"> <b class="fn">Sugar Art</b> <span class="says">says:</span> </div> <div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.homeandplate.com/blog/perfect-sugar-cookie-recipe/#comment-8759"><time datetime="2022-11-22T17:30:18+00:00">November 22, 2022 at 5:30 pm</time></a> </div> </footer> <div class="comment-content"> <p>Sweet and simple, just how we like it!</p> </div> </article> </li> </ul> <p class="no-comments">Comments are closed.</p> </div>  </div>   <div class="sidebar sidebar-column  col-md-3 "> <div class="sidebar-default-borders sidebar-block sidebar-borders"><div id="kale_aboutme_widget-2" class="default-widget widget widget-bordered widget_text"> <div class="kale-about-widget"> <h3 class="widget-title"><span>About Ali </span></h3><div class='textwidget'><div class='kale-about-widget-img'><img nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ilegjii.nitrocdn.com/bPcaZsOEGZoEcYkQXaTqQAgFcDxAlLBQ/assets/images/optimized/rev-ed5d556/www.homeandplate.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Ali-Randall-Home-and-Plate-recipes-headshot-e1548271860722.jpg" class="img-responsive pull-left nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTk3MToyODU=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTk3MToyODU=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDk5IDUzMSIgd2lkdGg9IjQ5OSIgaGVpZ2h0PSI1MzEiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+" /></div><div class='kale-about-widget-desc'><p>For everyday living, I like to prepare dishes that take little time, where the ingredients are easy to find at the local grocer and above all, taste good.</p> </div></div> </div> </div><div id="search-2" class="default-widget widget widget-bordered widget_search"><form role="search" method="get" class="search-form" action="https://www.homeandplate.com/"> <div class="form-group"> <input type="search" class="search-field form-control" value="" name="s" /> </div> <div class="form-actions"> <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Search</button> </div> </form> <span class="search-trigger"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></span> </div><div id="simple-social-icons-3" class="de